trailingComments.value:
*
     * Get the KKBOX authorization uri for user agreeing to authorize your application.
     *
     * @param {string} scope - ['user_profile', 'user_territory', 'user_account_status'] The scope of resource that developers ask KKBOX users to authorize.
     * @param {string} redirect_uri - The redirect URI for callback behavior of developer application.
     * @param {string} [response_type='code'] - The type of response.
     * @param {string} [state] - Developer may use this parameter freely.
     * @return {string} - Uri.
     * @example auth.authorizationCode.generateAuthorizationUri('user_profile user_territory user_account_status', 'https://text.com')
     * @see https://docs.kkbox.codes/docs/kkbox-oauth-20-authorize-api

trailingComments.value:
*
     * Fetch access token.
     *
     * @param {string} code - Get from the redirect uri's parameter. You set it while user agreeing to authorize your application then redirect to.
     * @return {Promise}
     * @example auth.authorizationCode.getAccessToken('029f6b352b21baf73290bd7ffaccd6f8')
     * @see https://docs.kkbox.codes/docs/oauth2-token-api-authorization-code-flow
